data.description:
New Price! Golf Lot - View! Welcome to the gated, golfing community of Turtle Creek consisting of 46 semi custom homes. This 3 bedroom, 2 bath beauty backs up to the golf course at the 12th hole. The bedrooms are arranged in a split plan for privacy, and a mini split A/C was added to the oversized primary suite for that perfectly
customized night's sleep. The open-concept common areas lead out to a spacious, screen-enclosed back porch that faces the golf course with a breezy ceiling
fan overhead. Interior offers a great room plan with open space, accent wall, premium kitchen and is great for entertaining. This property is approximately 1 mile to
